node.title: Rams beat Niners to take NFC title and secure spot in Super Bowl
node.description: The Rams will meet the Cincinnati Bengals in the Super Bowl on February 13.
node.content: ["The Los Angeles Rams have won the NFC Championship game, defeating the San Francisco 49ers 20-17. The Rams will play in the Super Bowl on\u00a0their home field against the Cincinnati Bengals on February 13.", "For Breaking News & Analysis Download the Free CBS News app"]
